SEI WALLET HEADS TO MILLIONS OF XIAOMI PHONES IN 2026

@SeiNetwork's wallet and crypto discovery app will come pre-installed on all new Xiaomi smartphones sold outside China and the US, giving $SEI direct exposure to the world's third-largest mobile vendor at 13% global market share.

The deal extends beyond the device. Stablecoin payments are launching across 20,000+ Xiaomi retail stores in Q2 2026, starting in Hong Kong and the EU. The Sei Foundation also committed $5M to a Global Mobile Innovation Program for builders.
